      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kaputzeja wiſſu to\nDraudſi/ pirmâ Deenâ/ ohtrâ\nMehneſi/ un lihdsinaja winno\nRaddus/ pehz winnu Sainehm/\npehz winno Tehwo Nammu/\nſkaitidami tohs Wahrduß no\nteem/ kas diwideſmits Gaddus\nun wehl wezzaki bija/ pehz winno\nGalwahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ittin ka tas KUNGS\nMohsum bija patwehſejis/ ta irr/\nwisch tohs flaitijis/ eekſch Si-\nnai Tuſtneses.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad bija Rubbena Behr-\nni/ Israeta Pirnidſimimuscha/\nwinno Raddi/ pehz winnu Sai-\nmehtm/ pehz winno Tehwo Nam-\nmeem/ furru Wahrdi ſkaititi\ntappe/ pehz winnu Galwahm/\nwiſſi no Wihra-Kahrtas/ no di-\nwideſmits Gaddeem un pahri/\nwiſſi/ kas Karra gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee/ kas no Rubbena\nZilts ſkaititi tappe/ bija tſchetr-\ndefinitis un ſetch tuhkſtochi/ un\npeeſſints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Sihmeanza Behrneem/\nwinnu Raddi/ pehz winnu Sai-\nmehtm/ pehz winno Tehwo Nam-\nmu/ kas no teem ſkaititi tappe/\npehz to Wahrdо Pulku/ pehz fa-\nwahm Galwahm/ wiſſi no Wih-\nra- Kahrtas/ no diwideſmits\nGaddeem un pahri/ wiſſi/ kas\nKarra gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee/ kas no tahs Sihme-\nana Zilts ſkaititi tappe/ bija peeẓ-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Gada Behrneem win-\nno Raddi/ pehz winnu Sai-\nmehni/ pehz winno Tehwo Nam-\nmu/ ka Wahrdi ſkaititi tappe/\nno diwideſmits Gaddeem un\npahri/ wiſſi/ kas Karra gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee/ kas no Gada Zilte-\nſkaititi tappe/ bija tſchetrdefinitis\npeez tuhkſtoschi/ ſeschſimts/ un\npeeẓdefinitis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Juhda Behrneem/\nwinnu Raddi/ pehz winnu Sai-\nmehni/ pehz winno Tehwu Nam-\nma/ ka Wahrdi ſkaititi tappe/ no\ndiwidesmits Gaddeem un pahri/\nwiſſi/ kas Karra gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee paſchi ſkaititi no Ju-\nda Zilts/ bija ſeptindefmits tſchet-\ntuhkſtoschi/ un ſeschſimts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Ihsaschara Behrneem/\nwinnu Raddi/ pehz winnu Sai-\nmehni/ pehz winno Tehwo\nNammu/ ka Wahrdi ſkaititi tap-\npe/ no diwideſmits Gaddeem\nun pahri/ wiſſi/ kas Karra gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee paſchi/ kas ſkaititi\ntappe/ no Ihsaschara Zilts/ bija\npeeẓdefinitis tſchetr tuhkſtochi/\nun tſchetrſimts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Sebulana Behrneem/\nwinno Raddi/ pehz winno Sai-\nmehni/ pehz winno Tehwo Nam-\nmu/ ka Wahrdi ſkaititi tappe no\ndiwideſmits Gaddeem un pahri/\nwiſſi/ kas Karra gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee paſchi ſkaititi no Se-\nbulana Zilts/ bija peeẓdefmitis ſep-\ntix tuhkſtoschi/ un tſchetrſimts.\n"
    }
  ],
